{"word":"ἐπισκέπτομαι","slug":"ἐπισκέπτομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπισϰέπτομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, σϰέπτομαι</el> ‘look about carefully’] ‘pay attention to’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> take an interest in <a href='B:650 2:6'>Hb 2:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on realizing an objective <b>look for, find <a href='B:510 6:1'>Ac 6</a>:</b>3. <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on effort to be helpful <b>look in on, visit <a href='B:470 25:36'>Mt 25:36</a>, <a href='B:470 25:43'>43</a>; <a href='B:510 7:23'>Ac 7:23</a>; <a href='B:510 15:36'>15:36</a>; <a href='B:660 1:27'>Js 1:27</a>.</b> Esp. of divine activity <b><a href='B:490 1:68'>Lk 1:68</a>, <a href='B:490 1:78'>78</a>; <a href='B:490 7:16'>7:16</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:510 15:14'>Ac 15:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπισιτισμός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπισκευάζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}